In this section, the term Indian tribe means any recognized Indian tribe included on the current list published by the Secretary of the Interior under 
              section 104 of the Federally Recognized Indian Tribe Act of 1994 (
              Public Law 103–454
            ; 108 Stat. 4792; 
              25 U.S.C. 479a–1
              ).

